176
00:11:55,738 --> 00:11:58,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK. I'll be fine.</font>

177
00:11:59,672 --> 00:12:02,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do your best at work, Uehara.</font>

178
00:12:03,672 --> 00:12:04,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I will.</font>

179
00:12:07,538 --> 00:12:08,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Bye.</font>

180
00:12:08,972 --> 00:12:09,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Bye.</font>

181
00:12:38,805 --> 00:12:40,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao!</font>

182
00:12:40,738 --> 00:12:41,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! Wake up!</font>

183
00:12:53,972 --> 00:12:54,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You OK?</font>

184
00:12:59,572 --> 00:13:01,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry, Issei.</font>

185
00:13:01,205 --> 00:13:02,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's OK. Lie back down.</font>

186
00:13:02,872 --> 00:13:06,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What about the shop?
-It's fine.</font>

187
00:13:06,438 --> 00:13:09,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Dad brought us here by car,
then he went back.</font>

188
00:13:09,772 --> 00:13:13,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see. Sorry.</font>

189
00:13:14,672 --> 00:13:17,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't believe you passed out.</font>

190
00:13:24,405 --> 00:13:27,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Issei?
-Yeah?</font>

191
00:13:29,072 --> 00:13:30,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Have you ever had a girlfriend?</font>

192
00:13:32,305 --> 00:13:34,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, yeah, sure.</font>

193
00:13:37,438 --> 00:13:39,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did you ever argue?</font>

194
00:13:39,538 --> 00:13:41,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Of course.</font>

195
00:13:44,572 --> 00:13:46,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did you ever think</font>

196
00:13:47,805 --> 00:13:51,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"I can't understand a woman's feelings"?</font>

197
00:13:51,538 --> 00:13:52,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You bet.</font>

198
00:13:55,538 --> 00:13:57,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

199
00:13:58,972 --> 00:14:00,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I guess it's only natural.</font>

200
00:14:02,605 --> 00:14:04,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Everyone probably thinks the same thing.</font>

201
00:14:10,572 --> 00:14:12,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, look,</font>

202
00:14:12,271 --> 00:14:15,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">if you can't understand
what a guy's thinking, then ask me.</font>

203
00:14:17,105 --> 00:14:18,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK?</font>

204
00:14:28,772 --> 00:14:30,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Once upon a time...</font>

205
00:14:31,039 --> 00:14:32,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

206
00:14:34,105 --> 00:14:38,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There was a couple that lived together.</font>

207
00:14:41,305 --> 00:14:43,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then suddenly, one day</font>

208
00:14:46,371 --> 00:14:49,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">the guy said
he wanted to live separately.</font>

209
00:14:49,638 --> 00:14:52,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Can you tell me why he said that?</font>

210
00:15:01,338 --> 00:15:02,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is that what Uehara said?</font>

211
00:15:07,171 --> 00:15:08,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's wrong with him?</font>

212
00:15:12,039 --> 00:15:13,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why did he say it?</font>

213
00:15:32,538 --> 00:15:34,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Because he...</font>

214
00:15:38,905 --> 00:15:40,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">stopped liking her.</font>

215
00:15:45,338 --> 00:15:47,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

216
00:15:53,238 --> 00:15:58,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought he was actually
asking to marry me.</font>

217
00:16:01,672 --> 00:16:03,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm such an idiot.</font>

218
00:16:06,205 --> 00:16:08,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How could you possibly think
he was asking you to marry him?</font>

219
00:16:38,772 --> 00:16:40,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Issei?</font>

220
00:16:49,405 --> 00:16:50,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

221
00:17:14,305 --> 00:17:16,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I didn't mean anything by that.</font>

222
00:17:18,872 --> 00:17:22,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You surprised me.</font>

223
00:17:35,972 --> 00:17:37,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know...</font>

224
00:17:40,271 --> 00:17:41,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes?</font>

225
00:17:42,238 --> 00:17:44,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want you to be mine.</font>

226
00:17:49,171 --> 00:17:50,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you joking again?</font>

227
00:18:07,039 --> 00:18:09,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Of course it's a joke. Don't be silly.</font>

228
00:18:12,872 --> 00:18:15,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, cut it out, Issei.</font>

229
00:18:16,505 --> 00:18:19,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, I'm going now.</font>

230
00:18:20,572 --> 00:18:22,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-OK.
-Bye.</font>

231
00:18:23,972 --> 00:18:27,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks so much, Issei.</font>

232
00:18:27,572 --> 00:18:28,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No problem.</font>

233
00:18:52,572 --> 00:18:53,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I brought her home.</font>

234
00:18:55,772 --> 00:18:57,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So her job comes with a free ride too?</font>

235
00:18:58,005 --> 00:18:59,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She fainted!</font>

236
00:19:00,205 --> 00:19:01,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

237
00:19:01,805 --> 00:19:04,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought I told you
not to make her cry.</font>

238
00:19:07,572 --> 00:19:09,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'd never let her cry like she does.</font>

239
00:19:12,538 --> 00:19:14,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Take good care of her, dammit.</font>

240
00:19:42,872 --> 00:19:43,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How are you feeling?</font>

241
00:19:45,972 --> 00:19:48,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Good. I'm just fine.</font>

242
00:19:58,572 --> 00:20:00,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello? Issei?</font>

243
00:20:03,105 --> 00:20:05,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'm going.
-Huh?</font>

244
00:20:11,072 --> 00:20:12,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks for yesterday.</font>

245
00:20:13,105 --> 00:20:16,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Take the day off today.
That's an order from your boss.</i></font>

246
00:20:33,472 --> 00:20:37,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Today, first period is self-study.</font>

247
00:20:37,338 --> 00:20:39,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Yes!
-All right!</font>

248
00:20:39,438 --> 00:20:42,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, quiet down! Quiet down!</font>

249
00:20:43,039 --> 00:20:45,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Nao.
-Yes?</font>

250
00:20:45,605 --> 00:20:47,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come with me to the counselling room.</font>

251
00:20:48,805 --> 00:20:49,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

252
00:20:50,171 --> 00:20:52,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">SELF-STUDY</font>

253
00:21:01,505 --> 00:21:02,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao and Uehara are living together.</font>

254
00:21:02,872 --> 00:21:04,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>We received this.</i></font>

255
00:21:05,105 --> 00:21:09,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And we've heard some rumors
that we cannot ignore.</font>

256
00:21:09,939 --> 00:21:11,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>When we hear rumors like this,</i></font>

257
00:21:12,039 --> 00:21:15,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">we have no choice
but to confirm their validity.</font>

258
00:21:15,205 --> 00:21:16,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Is it true that</i></font>

259
00:21:16,672 --> 00:21:21,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you're living with Yoshikawa Nao
of D class?</font>

260
00:21:21,939 --> 00:21:23,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well...</font>

261
00:21:25,672 --> 00:21:26,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes, it's true.</font>

262
00:21:27,538 --> 00:21:30,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We were the victims of fraud.</font>

263
00:21:32,039 --> 00:21:34,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>We didn't have the money to move...</i></font>

264
00:21:34,238 --> 00:21:37,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>So that's the reason
you couldn't help living together?</i></font>

265
00:21:37,905 --> 00:21:38,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

266
00:21:39,438 --> 00:21:42,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Do your parents know about this?</i></font>

267
00:21:45,538 --> 00:21:47,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I understand the situation clearly.</i></font>

268
00:21:47,438 --> 00:21:48,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">However, as a school,</font>

269
00:21:48,939 --> 00:21:52,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">we cannot give tacit approval to an
under-age boy and girl living together.</font>

270
00:21:52,805 --> 00:21:54,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think you understand.</font>

271
00:21:54,939 --> 00:21:55,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

272
00:21:55,839 --> 00:21:58,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>We're going to call your parents now,</i></font>

273
00:21:58,939 --> 00:22:01,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and ask them to come
to the school tomorrow.</font>

274
00:22:02,572 --> 00:22:05,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We'll decide what to do
after we talk to your parents.</font>

275
00:22:06,072 --> 00:22:07,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Do you understand?</i></font>

276
00:22:07,939 --> 00:22:09,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

277
00:22:11,105 --> 00:22:13,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry for causing this trouble.</font>

278
00:22:23,839 --> 00:22:25,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's from Uehara.</font>

279
00:22:26,972 --> 00:22:30,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">From: Uehara
I'll stay at my work tonight.</font>

280
00:22:41,205 --> 00:22:42,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's Mom.</font>

281
00:22:47,171 --> 00:22:48,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello?</font>

282
00:22:48,738 --> 00:22:50,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Nao?</i></font>

283
00:22:51,638 --> 00:22:56,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Is it still cold there?
Do I need to bring a coat?</i></font>

284
00:22:58,605 --> 00:23:02,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry about this, Mom.</font>

285
00:23:03,072 --> 00:23:07,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Don't worry. It will work out somehow.</i></font>

286
00:23:09,872 --> 00:23:11,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>But, Nao...</i></font>

287
00:23:12,605 --> 00:23:16,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I don't think you'll be able to
live there any longer.</i></font>

288
00:23:18,939 --> 00:23:20,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know.</font>

289
00:23:26,138 --> 00:23:27,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Evening Star Ramen!</font>

290
00:23:28,039 --> 00:23:30,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, it's the ramen. This way, please.</font>

291
00:23:30,705 --> 00:23:33,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, thank you.</font>

292
00:23:34,939 --> 00:23:39,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">About the bowls, I'm terribly sorry.</font>

293
00:23:39,271 --> 00:23:44,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's OK. Your father came and apologized
about that the other day.</font>

294
00:23:44,238 --> 00:23:47,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But it was me that broke them.</font>

295
00:23:47,505 --> 00:23:49,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I really am very, very sorry.</font>

296
00:23:50,271 --> 00:23:52,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, forget about it.</font>

297
00:23:52,238 --> 00:23:54,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll bring you payment.</font>

298
00:23:59,405 --> 00:24:04,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>So, Uehara, you've made up your mind?</i></font>

299
00:24:06,905 --> 00:24:10,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>If we keep living together like this
in secret,</i></font>

300
00:24:10,371 --> 00:24:12,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>it's only going to end up hurting her.</i></font>

301
00:24:37,105 --> 00:24:38,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Hello?</i></font>

302
00:24:39,171 --> 00:24:40,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's me.</font>

303
00:24:41,039 --> 00:24:42,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

304
00:24:43,138 --> 00:24:45,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Have you had dinner?</i></font>

305
00:24:47,405 --> 00:24:50,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah. And you?</font>

306
00:24:50,905 --> 00:24:52,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The landlady treated me to dinner.</font>

307
00:24:55,238 --> 00:24:58,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>So you're looking for a place?</i></font>

308
00:24:59,572 --> 00:25:03,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah. She said she could get me a place
pretty quickly.</font>

309
00:25:06,438 --> 00:25:10,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see. That's great.</font>

310
00:25:12,772 --> 00:25:16,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Yuri got called to the school
for tomorrow.</i></font>

311
00:25:18,772 --> 00:25:21,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri's back in Japan?</font>

312
00:25:22,271 --> 00:25:25,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Yeah. What about your parents?</i></font>

313
00:25:27,205 --> 00:25:28,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">They'll be at school tomorrow.</font>

314
00:25:31,338 --> 00:25:32,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

315
00:25:34,271 --> 00:25:37,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wonder what's going to happen to us.</font>

316
00:25:40,238 --> 00:25:41,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I have no idea either.</font>

317
00:25:45,338 --> 00:25:46,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara?</font>

318
00:25:47,839 --> 00:25:49,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah?</font>

319
00:25:54,072 --> 00:26:00,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do you... regret... living together?</font>

320
00:26:03,738 --> 00:26:04,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What about you?</font>

321
00:26:09,238 --> 00:26:13,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Not in the least. It surprises me.</font>

322
00:26:16,472 --> 00:26:19,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's because you hardly think
about it at all.</font>

323
00:26:21,171 --> 00:26:23,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're so mean!</font>

324
00:26:23,371 --> 00:26:26,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm thinking about it a lot.</font>

325
00:26:26,905 --> 00:26:27,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Liar.</i></font>

326
00:26:28,171 --> 00:26:30,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're even getting ready
to go to bed now.</font>

327
00:26:32,672 --> 00:26:34,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? How did...</font>

328
00:26:37,105 --> 00:26:41,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Go ahead. Get to bed. Talk to you later.</font>

329
00:26:41,572 --> 00:26:43,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait! Hold on--</font>

330
00:26:43,271 --> 00:26:44,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't regret it either.</font>

331
00:26:46,705 --> 00:26:47,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Bye.</font>

332
00:27:21,905 --> 00:27:23,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's go, Nao.</font>

333
00:27:23,572 --> 00:27:24,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

334
00:27:39,772 --> 00:27:42,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What's our next class?
-I'm not sure.</font>

335
00:27:48,939 --> 00:27:50,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Where is it?</font>

336
00:27:51,772 --> 00:27:53,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Nao.
-Huh?</font>

337
00:27:53,905 --> 00:27:56,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you looking for your key?</font>

338
00:27:59,039 --> 00:28:00,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

339
00:28:00,405 --> 00:28:02,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did it have a ribbon key holder?</font>

340
00:28:02,972 --> 00:28:04,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Give it back!</font>

341
00:28:04,305 --> 00:28:06,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's no way to ask.</font>

342
00:28:08,638 --> 00:28:09,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Where is it?</font>

343
00:28:10,538 --> 00:28:14,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Shiori found it on the floor,
so she's taking it to the police.</font>

344
00:28:27,505 --> 00:28:30,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara, Nao hasn't come back from P.E.</font>

345
00:28:31,138 --> 00:28:32,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

346
00:28:33,872 --> 00:28:36,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, Mitsuishi. Have you seen Nao?</font>

347
00:28:36,638 --> 00:28:39,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She ran out of here just a second ago.</font>

348
00:28:40,672 --> 00:28:42,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is something wrong?</font>

349
00:28:44,371 --> 00:28:45,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara!</font>

350
00:28:48,538 --> 00:28:50,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you really going to leave her?</font>

351
00:28:52,638 --> 00:28:53,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's none of your business.</font>

352
00:28:53,939 --> 00:28:56,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Yes, it is our business!
-That's right.</font>

353
00:28:56,405 --> 00:28:59,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We all want you two to be together.</font>

354
00:29:00,039 --> 00:29:03,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come on.
Try to understand why Nao's insecure.</font>

355
00:29:05,138 --> 00:29:07,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She can't tell what your feelings are
unless you tell her.</font>

356
00:29:20,972 --> 00:29:22,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Stop!</font>

357
00:29:23,039 --> 00:29:24,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Stop!</font>

358
00:29:25,171 --> 00:29:26,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Stop!</font>

359
00:29:29,039 --> 00:29:31,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Give me back my key.</font>

360
00:29:31,371 --> 00:29:32,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you talking about?</font>

361
00:29:33,171 --> 00:29:36,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's very important to me. Give it back.</font>

362
00:29:42,438 --> 00:29:45,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's no way
you two are living together!</font>

363
00:29:50,738 --> 00:29:52,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh-oh.</font>

364
00:30:04,505 --> 00:30:07,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm terribly sorry for all this trouble.</font>

365
00:30:07,305 --> 00:30:08,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please have a seat.</font>

366
00:30:12,738 --> 00:30:14,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'd like you to look at these.</font>

367
00:30:25,839 --> 00:30:29,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Can you believe her?
She's lost her mind.</font>

368
00:30:33,538 --> 00:30:35,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's cold!</font>

369
00:30:46,605 --> 00:30:49,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>She is my girlfriend.</i></font>

370
00:30:49,905 --> 00:30:51,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Lean on others when you need to.</i></font>

371
00:30:52,738 --> 00:30:56,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Don't worry. I'm not interested
in anyone but you right now.</i></font>

372
00:30:57,039 --> 00:30:59,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Uehara, I like you.</i></font>

373
00:31:03,605 --> 00:31:05,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I'll treasure it forever.</i></font>

374
00:31:06,438 --> 00:31:10,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>"Absence makes the heart grow fonder."</i></font>

375
00:31:10,305 --> 00:31:12,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>There you go crying again.</i></font>

376
00:31:25,005 --> 00:31:29,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>You mean to tell me
that you knew they were living together?</i></font>

377
00:31:29,505 --> 00:31:32,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes, of course we did.</font>

378
00:31:44,072 --> 00:31:45,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What the hell are you doing, Nao?</font>

379
00:31:50,505 --> 00:31:51,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao!</font>

380
00:31:53,338 --> 00:31:54,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My key!</font>

381
00:31:54,738 --> 00:31:58,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If I lose that,
then it really <i>will be all over.</i></font>

382
00:32:00,672 --> 00:32:02,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Stop this and calm down!</font>

383
00:32:05,005 --> 00:32:06,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let go of me!</font>

384
00:32:16,505 --> 00:32:17,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao!</font>

385
00:32:22,605 --> 00:32:23,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I...</font>

386
00:32:29,138 --> 00:32:30,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I lied to you.</font>

387
00:32:32,205 --> 00:32:33,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

388
00:32:38,505 --> 00:32:41,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The real reason a guy says
he wants to live separately</font>

389
00:32:41,572 --> 00:32:43,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">is that he doesn't want to hurt the girl.</font>

390
00:33:02,405 --> 00:33:04,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you, Issei.</font>

391
00:33:30,371 --> 00:33:31,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello?</font>

392
00:33:52,105 --> 00:33:56,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The situation was really very complex.</font>

393
00:33:56,605 --> 00:33:59,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We worried over it
quite a bit ourselves.</font>

394
00:33:59,371 --> 00:34:03,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And we talked it over good
and long with our daughter.</font>

395
00:34:04,238 --> 00:34:08,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I still don't think
living together was a solution.</font>

396
00:34:08,738 --> 00:34:11,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">They're only 17.
And they're a boy and a girl.</font>

397
00:34:14,605 --> 00:34:16,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm...</font>

398
00:34:17,538 --> 00:34:20,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-It's not just the two of them alone.
-Really?</font>

399
00:34:20,738 --> 00:34:22,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm living with them too.</font>

400
00:34:23,405 --> 00:34:24,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't understand.</font>

401
00:34:25,238 --> 00:34:28,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara's older brother is my husband.
He's working overseas now.</font>

402
00:34:28,972 --> 00:34:32,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So I'm living with Uehara
and Nao here in Japan.</font>

403
00:34:32,839 --> 00:34:35,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's more like Nao is boarding with us.</font>

404
00:34:36,538 --> 00:34:39,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So it's not just those two alone?</font>

405
00:34:39,638 --> 00:34:42,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, of course not!
They're only high-school kids.</font>

406
00:34:42,238 --> 00:34:43,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then what about these?</font>

407
00:34:43,205 --> 00:34:45,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, there's a lot of that.</font>

408
00:34:45,438 --> 00:34:48,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara's fans always
make a mountain out of a molehill.</font>

409
00:34:48,171 --> 00:34:51,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-He really is handsome, isn't he?
-You think so?</font>

410
00:34:51,738 --> 00:34:52,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, please.</font>

411
00:34:52,672 --> 00:34:55,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't tell me that you were fooled
into thinking this was true?</font>

412
00:34:55,638 --> 00:34:57,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, we weren't taken in.</font>

413
00:34:57,538 --> 00:34:59,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, of course you weren't.</font>

414
00:34:59,638 --> 00:35:01,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">However, due to these rumors,</font>

415
00:35:01,839 --> 00:35:05,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">we'll have to ask
that she stop living there.</font>

416
00:35:05,472 --> 00:35:08,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-We don't want other students to see.
-I see.</font>

417
00:35:08,171 --> 00:35:11,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We've already decided on moving her out.</font>

418
00:35:12,371 --> 00:35:16,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh my god. She's still at it.
-What an idiot.</font>

419
00:35:17,138 --> 00:35:18,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is hilarious.</font>

420
00:35:18,705 --> 00:35:20,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think I'll just start sending this out.</font>

421
00:35:20,572 --> 00:35:23,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I heard Nao's parents were called in
by the vice principal.</font>

422
00:35:23,538 --> 00:35:26,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Seriously?
-Because of this.</font>

423
00:35:26,572 --> 00:35:27,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah! That!</font>

424
00:35:27,738 --> 00:35:31,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That really sent the teachers
into a panic.</font>

425
00:35:33,039 --> 00:35:34,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you doing?</font>

426
00:35:35,305 --> 00:35:36,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey!</font>

427
00:35:36,238 --> 00:35:37,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I couldn't care less anymore.</font>

428
00:35:38,271 --> 00:35:39,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

429
00:35:41,005 --> 00:35:45,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I couldn't care less about Uehara
or her anymore.</font>

430
00:35:47,271 --> 00:35:48,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's go.</font>

431
00:35:50,438 --> 00:35:52,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I guess she thinks
she doesn't have a chance with him.</font>

432
00:35:54,939 --> 00:35:57,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, wait up.</font>

433
00:36:03,005 --> 00:36:05,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! Nao!</font>

434
00:36:06,438 --> 00:36:08,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What are you doing?
-Uehara.</font>

435
00:36:12,039 --> 00:36:16,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I lost my key, Uehara.</font>

436
00:36:18,105 --> 00:36:19,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait! My key.</font>

437
00:36:19,205 --> 00:36:23,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao... let's go home.</font>

438
00:36:24,738 --> 00:36:26,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-But--
-Don't worry about it.</font>

439
00:36:42,138 --> 00:36:43,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

440
00:36:44,905 --> 00:36:48,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Nao?
-Yes?</font>

441
00:36:48,171 --> 00:36:51,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Could you tell me why you thought
I was asking you to marry me?</font>

442
00:36:53,872 --> 00:36:54,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

443
00:36:55,271 --> 00:36:58,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No matter how much I think about it,
I can't figure it out.</font>

444
00:37:03,305 --> 00:37:05,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, you're right.</font>

445
00:37:05,105 --> 00:37:08,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Now that I think about it,
I don't know what I was thinking.</font>

446
00:37:09,238 --> 00:37:12,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I let myself get all carried away.</font>

447
00:37:14,839 --> 00:37:17,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Were you really that happy about it?</font>

448
00:37:18,805 --> 00:37:20,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Of course I was happy.</font>

449
00:37:30,438 --> 00:37:31,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">However...</font>

450
00:37:33,939 --> 00:37:36,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">even though
that wasn't my meaning then...</font>

451
00:37:41,405 --> 00:37:42,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I...</font>

452
00:37:45,438 --> 00:37:47,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I <i>do want to be with you forever.</i></font>

453
00:37:50,472 --> 00:37:54,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't know what the future holds,
but that's how I feel right now.</font>

454
00:37:57,405 --> 00:38:01,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Even if it's not here,
and even if we live separately,</font>

455
00:38:03,572 --> 00:38:05,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">let's be together forever.</font>

456
00:38:43,472 --> 00:38:44,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

457
00:39:35,371 --> 00:39:37,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So you're going to move.</font>

458
00:39:38,205 --> 00:39:40,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll miss you.</font>

459
00:39:41,572 --> 00:39:42,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm...</font>

460
00:39:45,072 --> 00:39:47,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I have another favor to ask you.</font>

461
00:39:48,605 --> 00:39:50,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come in.</font>

462
00:39:50,138 --> 00:39:52,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Long time no see!
-Daichi! Nice to see you!</font>

463
00:39:52,872 --> 00:39:53,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come in.</font>

464
00:39:53,872 --> 00:39:54,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Is everyone here?
-Yeah.</font>

465
00:39:55,039 --> 00:39:57,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, long time no see.</font>

466
00:39:57,138 --> 00:39:58,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Daichi!
-Hi!</font>

467
00:39:59,238 --> 00:40:02,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That university smell
makes you even more handsome.</font>

468
00:40:02,805 --> 00:40:04,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Really?
-Yes.</font>

469
00:40:04,772 --> 00:40:05,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hi.</font>

470
00:40:06,105 --> 00:40:07,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-It's been a while.
-Who's that? Introduce me.</font>

471
00:40:07,839 --> 00:40:09,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're just a kid still.</font>

472
00:40:09,171 --> 00:40:11,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you talking about?
Come on, introduce me.</font>

473
00:40:11,605 --> 00:40:13,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here you go. It's ready.</font>

474
00:40:14,039 --> 00:40:15,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's shrimp.</font>

475
00:40:15,072 --> 00:40:19,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Look at you!
You're as handsome as ever, Daichi!</font>

476
00:40:21,371 --> 00:40:23,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's handsome too.
Who's that? Introduce me.</font>

477
00:40:23,705 --> 00:40:26,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How come she's not asking who I am?</font>

478
00:40:26,171 --> 00:40:27,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's ignoring me too.</font>

479
00:40:33,538 --> 00:40:34,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

480
00:40:42,772 --> 00:40:44,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you!</font>

481
00:40:46,605 --> 00:40:48,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do you want some pot stickers?</font>

482
00:40:49,538 --> 00:40:51,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you. Here's the soy sauce.</font>

483
00:40:51,872 --> 00:40:53,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks. Pour some on.</font>

484
00:40:54,305 --> 00:40:58,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's time to propose a toast
to Uehara and Nao's future together.</font>

485
00:40:58,338 --> 00:41:00,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait! Is that alcohol?</font>

486
00:41:00,305 --> 00:41:02,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't be such a wet blanket.</font>

487
00:41:02,638 --> 00:41:04,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK. Cheers!</font>

488
00:41:04,538 --> 00:41:07,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Cheers!
-Cheers!</font>

489
00:41:21,905 --> 00:41:23,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>My lease here starts from today.</i></font>

490
00:41:23,905 --> 00:41:26,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you talking about?
Look, Room 305!</font>

491
00:41:26,405 --> 00:41:28,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Me too, Room 305!</font>

492
00:41:29,872 --> 00:41:30,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh?
-Huh?</font>

493
00:41:39,138 --> 00:41:40,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you packed?</font>

494
00:41:42,638 --> 00:41:43,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yep.</font>

495
00:41:43,738 --> 00:41:45,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Polar Bear Moving!</i></font>

496
00:41:46,538 --> 00:41:48,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Coming.
-Coming.</font>

497
00:42:03,338 --> 00:42:05,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, I'll see you.</font>

498
00:42:06,105 --> 00:42:07,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah.</font>

499
00:42:08,405 --> 00:42:10,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The truck is that way.</font>

500
00:42:11,072 --> 00:42:12,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mine's that way.</font>

501
00:42:13,538 --> 00:42:14,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

502
00:42:16,638 --> 00:42:17,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Bye.</font>

503
00:42:18,805 --> 00:42:19,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Bye.</font>

504
00:42:33,405 --> 00:42:34,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara!</font>

505
00:42:48,772 --> 00:42:49,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry. It's nothing.</font>

506
00:42:52,772 --> 00:42:54,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">See you.</font>

507
00:43:04,072 --> 00:43:04,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao!</font>

508
00:43:27,772 --> 00:43:29,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I love you.</font>

509
00:43:50,605 --> 00:43:52,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know.</font>

510
00:44:03,772 --> 00:44:07,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Room 305 is vacant now.</font>

511
00:44:08,672 --> 00:44:12,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But there's a condition
regarding the length of the lease.</font>

512
00:44:12,072 --> 00:44:14,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">SQUIRREL MOVERS</font>

513
00:44:21,805 --> 00:44:23,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here goes!</font>

514
00:44:30,505 --> 00:44:31,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you. Good bye.</font>

515
00:44:35,039 --> 00:44:35,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ah!</font>

516
00:44:38,538 --> 00:44:39,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry!</font>

517
00:44:47,772 --> 00:44:49,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

518
00:44:51,072 --> 00:44:52,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why are you here?</font>

519
00:44:53,772 --> 00:44:55,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why am I here?</font>

520
00:44:55,672 --> 00:44:57,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Because this is where I live now.</font>

521
00:44:58,872 --> 00:44:59,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm in 402.</font>

522
00:45:01,638 --> 00:45:02,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

523
00:45:03,305 --> 00:45:04,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Where are you?</font>

524
00:45:06,572 --> 00:45:10,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm... in 401.</font>

525
00:45:12,138 --> 00:45:14,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh... do you think...</font>

526
00:45:16,072 --> 00:45:17,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-the landlady did this?
-the landlady did this?</font>

527
00:45:22,005 --> 00:45:24,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I have another favor to ask.</i></font>

528
00:45:25,672 --> 00:45:30,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Three years from now
when we're adults,</font>

529
00:45:32,171 --> 00:45:34,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'd like to move back into that place...</font>

530
00:45:35,705 --> 00:45:36,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>with her.</i></font>

531
00:45:37,371 --> 00:45:38,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">RENTAL AGREEMENT</font>

532
